All Packages

Package Summary 
Package Description
com.mhealthatlas.apps
com.mhealthatlas.apps contains all functionalities of the application service.
com.mhealthatlas.apps.command
com.mhealthatlas.apps.command is a group of services which only mutate data but have not advanced query functionalities.
com.mhealthatlas.apps.config
com.mhealthatlas.apps.config contains the service configuration.
com.mhealthatlas.apps.config.kafka
com.mhealthatlas.apps.config.kafka contains the kafka specific configuration of the service.
com.mhealthatlas.apps.config.web
com.mhealthatlas.apps.config.web contains the web specific configuration of the service.
com.mhealthatlas.apps.config.web.filter
com.mhealthatlas.apps.config.web contains the definition of custom filter used in the filter pipeline for HTTP requests.
com.mhealthatlas.apps.controller
com.mhealthatlas.apps.controller is a group of REST API controllers in the application service.
Each class ending with the QueryController prefix provides GET API endpoints for quering application information.
Each class ending with the CommandController prefix provides POST and DELETE API endpoints for mutating the application information state.
com.mhealthatlas.apps.dto
com.mhealthatlas.apps.dto contains all data transfer object definitions.
com.mhealthatlas.apps.helper
com.mhealthatlas.apps.helper is a group of static utility methods to convert the entity object to the dto representation.
com.mhealthatlas.apps.model
com.mhealthatlas.apps.model contains all entities form the application service database and the enum declarations.
com.mhealthatlas.apps.properties
com.mhealthatlas.apps.properties contains the custom service properties.
com.mhealthatlas.apps.query
com.mhealthatlas.apps.query is a group of services which only queries data but does not mutate them.
com.mhealthatlas.apps.receiver
com.mhealthatlas.apps.receiver contains all kafka event listener.
com.mhealthatlas.apps.repository
com.mhealthatlas.apps.repository contains all repository interfaces of the application service.
com.mhealthatlas.apps.search
com.mhealthatlas.apps.search contains functions to parse and tokenize a search query.
